name: The last serving
description: Many people create harmful content in order to gain popularity on social media. Not infrequently the creation of content that ends in death. there is a video on social media of a person making a video of eating large amounts of food and leading to death because the heart is not functioning and the organs are full of food, this disorder is a serious condition related to eating behavior that has a negative impact on health, emotions, and ability to function. This condition is included in mental illness. As a result, it can harm the heart, this is only a small picture and maybe a simple "eat", many more reckless and crazy things they do just for the sake of popularity, this painting depicts a human head with a tongue sticking out and choking, his body filled with lust and unable to control people who watch can laugh and amaze at temporary pleasure, the message of this painting, control yourself we can do many things that amaze other people but every human being has limits.
